Package ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.GUI.OrgUnitMembersandLeader

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AccountTabGUI
    Tab panel for the OrgUnitMemGUI, displaying account information
    AssetDetailGUI
    AssetDetailGUI is opened whenever an asset is selected and the view asset button is pressed It displays buy and sell offers for that particular asset, allows the user to make buy and sell offers for that asset and also displays a price history chart for it
    BuyTabGUI
    BuyTabGUI class is responsible for displaying the organisational unit's buy offers and all the market buy offers Enables user to remove their org's offers and view assets on the market
    Helper
    Helper Class for creating certain JComponents
    MarketplaceHistoryGraph
    Class for creating a graph for the marketplace history, x-axis is the date, y-axis is the float price
    OrgUnitMemGUI
    The container with the buy, sell, org unit, and account tabs for the organisational unit member GUI
    OrgUnitTabGUI
    GUI for displaying details about the organisational unit: its trade history, assets it owns, and members of the unit
    SellTabGUI
    SellTabGUI class is responsible for displaying the organisational unit's sell offers and all the market sell offers Enables user to remove their org's offers and view assets on the market
